record_data.record_plain_text: WABASH VALLEY POWER ASSOCIATION, INC. Reactive Supply and Voltage Control Tariff - PJM FERC Electric Tariff Volume No. 4 Wabash Valley Power Association, Inc. Reactive Supply and Voltage Control from Generation Sources Service Wabash Valley Power Association, Inc. ("WVPA") provides Reactive Supply and Voltage from Generation Sources Service ("Reactive Supply Service") from the generating sources listed below to the PJM Interconnection, LLC ("PJM") system. This Rate Schedule sets forth WVPA's revenue requirements for the provision of Reactive Supply Service to PJM, as contemplated by Schedule 2 of the PJM open access transmission tariff. This Rate Schedule shall be effective upon the date authorized by the Federal Energy Regulatory Commission.
